    "EduLLMs (educational LLMs) are fundamental to these paradigms, as they enable tasks like semantic understanding, sentiment analysis, and text comprehension [3,25].",
    "By analyzing large datasets, EduLLMs can provide real-time question answering and extract meaningful insights to aid learning.",
    "Deep learning techniques like Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) further enhance their output quality [26,27].",
    "Hybrid deep learning techniques have been used to analyze student academic performance [28] as well as exam supervision [29].Incorporating Reinforcement Learning into EduLLMs enables models to adapt to student feedback dynamically, improving performance over time [30].",
